title: Table 157 - Row 7
clause_text: Sr. No. (1): 4 | Occupancy (2): Government or semi- public or private office business buildings | Parking Space required (3): One parking space for every 37.5 sq. m of office space up to 1500 sq. m and for every 75-sq.m of additional space for areas exceeding 1500 sq. m in other areas.
